Package problem01.controller

Class TaskManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • problem01.controller.TaskManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITaskManager
    public class TaskManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITaskManager
    Acts as an invoker class in the Command design pattern. Stores a list of all tasks to be performed, as well as methods for creating and performing these tasks.
